            "color": "#333",
            "bgcolor": "#1a1a1a",
            "title": "4. Prompt: ES-2 Character Sheet",
            "properties": {
              "text": "{\n  \"format\": \"plain_text\",\n  \"reference_input\": \"Approved portrait from step 1 (es2-step1-portrait)\",\n  \"character_reference\": {\n    \"instruction\": \"Use the attached portrait as the absolute ground truth for the subject's facial features, skin texture, and bone structure. The face in all three views must be a 1:1 match of the portrait provided.\",\n    \"face\": {\n      \"preserve_original\": true\n    }\n  },\n  \"prompt\": \"A character reference sheet of a Latino man in his late twenties, warm medium tan skin, dark brown almost black hair with a clean tapered fade on the sides and longer textured top swept to one side, thick dark eyebrows with a natural arch, striking vivid green eyes, strong angular jawline, high cheekbones, straight nose, clean shaven. Three vertically stacked photos filling the entire frame edge to edge with no gaps, no borders, no dividing lines between them. Top third: front facing headshot, relaxed neutral expression, looking directly at camera. Middle third: three quarter view, head turned slightly to the right. Bottom third: full side profile facing right. All three shots are shoulders up, wearing a fitted dark charcoal grey athletic t shirt that stretches across broad muscular shoulders and defined arms. Black fitness tracker on left wrist. No makeup, natural bare skin. Shot on a smartphone against a plain light grey wall, natural window light from the left, social media realism. --ar 9:16 --no borders, frames, dividing lines, white space between photos, text, labels, tattoos, jewelry, brown eyes, facial hair, beard, stubble, patterns on clothing, 3d render\",\n  \"notes\": \"This sheet becomes the MASTER character reference for all future images. Attach the approved step 1 portrait as the reference image input when generating.\"\n}\n",
